#: ../../packaging.md:1
msgid "Bundlers and Koffi"
msgstr "打包工具和Koffi"

#: ../../packaging.md:3
msgid "Bundling and native modules"
msgstr "打包原生模块"

#: ../../packaging.md:5
msgid "*Simplified in Koffi 2.5.9*"
msgstr "*自Koffi 2.5.9起简化了*"

#: ../../packaging.md:7
msgid ""
"Koffi uses native modules to work. The NPM package contains binaries for "
"various platforms and architectures, and the appropriate module is "
"selected at runtime."
msgstr ""
"Koffi需要原生模块来工作. NPM包中含有不同平台和架构的二进制, 会在运行时中选择合适的模块."

#: ../../packaging.md:9
msgid ""
"In theory, the **packagers/bundlers should be able to find all native "
"modules** because they are explictly listed in the Javascript file (as "
"static strings) and package them somehow."
msgstr ""
"理论上, 由于它们都被显式地列在Javascript文件中(以静态字符串), **打包工具应当能直接找到所有原生模块**并以某种方式打包它们."

#: ../../packaging.md:11
msgid ""
"If that is not the case, you can manually arrange to copy the "
"`node_modules/koffi/build/koffi` directory next to your bundled script."
msgstr ""
"如果没有成功, 你可以手动将`node_modules/koffi/build/koffi`复制到你打包后的脚本旁."

